*************************************
               README
*************************************
This is the README for smss.
*************************************
            DEPENDENCIES
*************************************
You'll need:
1. wxpython (http://wxpython.org/)
2. pycurl	(http://pycurl.sourceforge.net/)
3. curl		(http://curl.haxx.se/download.html)

If on Ubuntu (or its derivative), then run the following to install dependencies.

	sudo apt-get install curl libnotify-bin python-wxgtk2.8 python-wxtools wx2.8-i18n install python-gdata
*************************************
            INSTALLATION
*************************************

To install smss, run the following:

	cd <this directory>
	make
	sudo make install
	

*************************************
              REMOVAL
*************************************
For removing, run the following commands:
	
	sudo rm /usr/bin/smss
	sudo -R rm /usr/share/smss
	
If that doesn't work, then run:
	
	su
	rm /usr/bin/smss
	rm -R /usr/share/smss

Then run:
	rm ~/.gnome2/nautilus-scripts/Upload\ To\ Facebook

For removing configuration files, run:
	rm -R ~/.smss
	
*************************************
         RUNNING smss
*************************************
To run, go to Applications>>Internet>>SMSS

If that doesn't work, run
	smss
from the terminal or a run dialog.

